# 标准资源管理接口测试文档

### 获取验证码
GET http://localhost:8080/security/imageCaptcha
Content-Type: application/json

### 用户登录 (需要先获取验证码，然后手动输入验证码)
# POST http://localhost:8080/security/login
# Content-Type: application/json
# 
# {
#   "utext": "dGVzdA==",
#   "ptext": "MTIzNDU2",
