### 4. 根据ID查询标准资源详情 (需要先获取实际ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/{{resourceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 根据标准编号查询标准资源
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/code/GB/T 14396-2024
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 根据标准状态查询标准资源列表
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/listByStatus?standardStatus=现行
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 根据标准领域查询标准资源列表
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/listByField?standardField=医疗
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 根据标准分类查询标准资源列表
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/listByClassification?standardClassification=数据元
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 获取标准状态选项
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/statusOptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 获取标准领域选项
GET http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/fieldOptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. 批量删除标准资源 (删除第一条数据，需要先获取实际ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/standard/resource/deleteBatch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

["{{resourceId1}}"]

### 测试步骤说明：
# 1. 首先运行获取验证码接口
# 2. 复制返回的checkCodeKey
# 3. 查看验证码图片，输入验证码
# 4. 运行登录接口获取token
# 5. 将token填入上面的{{token}}位置
# 6. 按顺序执行标准资源管理接口测试